metadata.name: Angry Ape Army Valkyrie #0001
metadata.description: ...dark silhouettes emerged over the smoke filled horizon giving the Angry Ape Army their first sliver of hope. As the shadows grew closer, it became clear the tides had turned. The long-awaited Valkyrie warriors stormed the battlefield, reuniting with the Angry Ape Army and claiming victory once and for all. This token represents a Valkyrie that is metaverse compatible with access to claims and more. Join the fight today... all hail Valkyries!
